name: Josephi Krakowski IN the stolen Гибкая лента
name_original: Josephi Krakowski IN the stolen Гибкая лента
description: Josephi Krakowski was working on his newest project called  Гибкая лента (Flex tape in Russian) when all of a sudden, Phil Swift's clones came out of nowhere and stole the Гибкая лента prototype, now you must control Josephi to get it back.
